file=Brand Studio/weave/custom/brand-story-arcs/assets/chapter-registry-template.md · [nc:[Brand Name] Chapter Registry — TEMPLATE (the continuity ledger)=> One line per chapter told. Append-only (corrections by reference — precedent's discipline\n> applied to narrative). This ledger is what makes the story CUMULATIVE: continuity checks\n> run against it, repeats get caught by it, and canon changes get logged in it.\n> A chapter = one narrative beat, which may span many posts/assets (pulse serializes;\n> the ledger tracks chapters, not posts).\n\n**Brand:** [name] \· **Arc version in force:** [vX.Y]\n · tb=\| # \| Date \| Chapter (one line) \| Act \| Element advanced \| Canon facts added \| Campaign/assets \| Verdict trail \| · tb=\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\| · tb=\| 1 \| \| \| I \| villain / hero-struggle / guide-proof / promised-land / world-change \| \| \| ON-ARC \| · tb=\| Date \| From → To \| What changed (new act / canon fact / retired element) \| Rationale (one line) \| Adopted by \| · tb=\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\| · dc:Deliberate callbacks=[Retellings are allowed only as named callbacks — list them so they read as craft, not amnesia.]\n · tb=\| Date \| Calls back to chapter # \| Why \| · tb=\|---\|---\|---\|